akn:content.akn:p:
§§ 1091 to 1094. Repealed. Pub. L. 94–265, title IV, § 402(a), Apr. 13, 1976, 90 Stat. 360
Sections, Pub. L. 89–658, §§ 1–4, Oct. 14, 1966, 80 Stat. 908, set out provisions authorizing the establishment of a fishery zone contiguous to the territorial sea of the United States. See section 1801 et seq. of this title.
Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries Effective Date of RepealPub. L. 94–265, title IV, § 402(a), Apr. 13, 1976, 90 Stat. 360, provided that repeal of sections 1091 to 1094 of this title is effective Mar. 1, 1977.
